  "texts": [
    "Interestingly, GCG's performance drops to 0 when transferred to GPT-4, likely due to additional safety measures in OpenAI's more advanced models after they released their paper.",
    "Notably, although GCG, GBDA, and ARCA are optimized directly on Llama-2 7b Chat, none of them match our PAP's ASR on Llama-2.",
    "This suggests that while Llama-2 may have been aligned to defend these established algorithm-focused attacks, their safety measures might have underestimated the jailbreak risks coming from natural communication with everyday users.",
    "A side note is that all the evaluated jailbreak methods perform poorly on the Claude models, indicating a distinct safety measure difference between Claude's and other model families.",
    "Llama-2 GPT-3."
